     On July 12, 2007, Big 5 Sporting Goods Corporation (the "Company") issued a press release in which the Company announced its net sales and same-store sales results for, and updated certain guidance for, its fiscal 2007 second quarter. The press release is furnished as Exhibit 99.1 to this Current Report on Form 8-K.
