     On January 10, 2008, Big 5 Sporting Goods Corporation (the "Company") issued a press release in which the Company, among other things, reported its net sales and same-store sales results for its fiscal 2007 fourth quarter and full fiscal year. The press release is furnished as Exhibit 99.1 to this Current Report on Form 8-K.
